name: TARS Protocol
description: TARS Protocol is an AI-driven, scalable Web3 modular infrastructure platform designed to empower projects with cutting-edge artificial intelligence solutions and one-stop BaaS (Blockchain-as-a-Service). TARS aims to bridge the gap between AI and Web3 worlds by providing a unified platform for AI-powered tools and services, enabling organizations and individuals to effortlessly transition from Web2 to Web3.
